sentences.sContent: Denmark also has 2 autonomous provinces – the Faroe Islands and Greenland.
sentences.sCn: 丹麦也有2个自治区——法罗群岛和格陵兰。

sentences.sContent: Representatives from 17 countries and territories, including the United States and the Faroe Islands (also owned by Denmark), were there.
sentences.sCn: 来自17个国家和地区的代表，包括美国和同属丹麦的法罗群岛都在场。

trans.tranCn: 法罗群岛（位于丹麦北大西洋）
